{"tid":567102,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(蓋清領導潮流）時下最興嘅窒息遊戲，Yoyo 一早已經玩緊","createTime":"2018-02-20T14:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T11:50:11.000Z","uid":1426,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1ee953a97f339f99f11803b31d3a5366ee4aad20","tid":567102,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:18:58.000Z","msg":"Yoyo就用手同我打起Ｊ來，就喺我可以發射嘅時侯，佢用手蓋住我個鼻孔，令我呼吸急喘起來，再而用雙手摙實我條頸，摙到我上氣唔接下氣又鬆手比我吸氣，此舉真係要有番咁上下ＳＭ技藝嘅高手至玩得到，Yoyo佢對時間同力量控制到剛剛好，就好似一個大廚司一樣，識得控制火喉至得架，所謂萬事俱備，只欠一個識玩ＳＭ嘅；我！一定揀Yoyo！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/221852_9d7291a5c179fac1093e6afc371e70c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F221852_9d7291a5c179fac1093e6afc371e70c8.png&h=bc31371c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/221854_dd807e9ef44b0609c54a5a04621b499d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F221854_dd807e9ef44b0609c54a5a04621b499d.png&h=86962703&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/221856_94e46343faeebd41661063da6bea57bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F221856_94e46343faeebd41661063da6bea57bb.png&h=e75866f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"345fbd11eec91368087397d2345ccc9444e8d108","tid":567102,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:20:06.000Z","msg":"一直以來各地流行一種「窒息遊戲」，青少年為追求刺激，以狗帶、繩索或索帶套在自己頸上，阻止血液流向腦部，幾乎窒息時將索帶鬆開，令血液迅間衝上腦部，從而產生快感。然而，過去不少青少年因此意外喪命。 <br />\n<br />\n根據美國疾控中心2008年的研究報告指，全國將近兩成青少年玩過窒息遊戲，於1995至2007年間有82名兒童（6至19歲）因此死亡，但美國官員坦言數字低估實際情況，因部分案件難以確認是玩窒息遊戲抑或蓄意自殺。於2012年，美國加州一名15歲少年玩窒息遊戲缺氧瀕臨失去意識倒下時，撞破一個玻璃杯，玻璃碎片插入頸動脈喪命。同年美國威州一名12歲少年，亦因此遊戲窒息致死。"},{"pid":"370ba7d8ba471f322db00db47c191d8609a5c385","tid":567102,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d990d699964bcde4916ed6ddcec189aaa24ca093","tid":567102,"uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"370ba7d8ba471f322db00db47c191d8609a5c385","tid":567102,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:22:15.000Z","msg":"真個蓋清已經窒息死咗，呢到呢個劣質嘅係假貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0bf1221d90cc8472e8917c348dac2ca34ef24d","tid":567102,"uid":1426,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/FWNalm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FFWNalm.gif&h=e9430b66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d32da9e0bbfd2dfeff898f7478262d0feb21ffb","tid":567102,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T15:15:03.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"c4b533273044680ba0b3623c5e04f3564a32b61c","tid":567102,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T15:27:33.000Z","msg":"屎水"},{"pid":"9ec5ea3a1e96bd4633627b435f6d4a7eb79afba2","tid":567102,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d990d699964bcde4916ed6ddcec189aaa24ca093","tid":567102,"uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"370ba7d8ba471f322db00db47c191d8609a5c385","tid":567102,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:22:15.000Z","msg":"真個蓋清已經窒息死咗，呢到呢個劣質嘅係假貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"rep